STATE
v.
Keyshawn JONES. No. 27PA16-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 12, 2016. John F. Carella, Assistant Appellate Defender, for Jones, Keyshawn. Rajeev K. Premakumar, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. Robert C. Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. Matthew Delbridge, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

The following order has been entered on the Motion for Extension of Time to File Brief filed on the 12th of May 2016 by State of NC:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference, this the 12th of May 2016."

State of NC shall have up to and including the 15th day of June 2016 to file and serve his/her brief with this Court.
